<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Form Submission</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #e9844c; /* Horizon's primary color */
            padding: 30px 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 30px 24px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666666;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin: 0;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #e9844c; /* Horizon's primary color */
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .details {
            background-color: #eef2ff; /* Light blue background from Horizon */
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .details p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .details strong {
            color: #4f46e5; /* Horizon's secondary color for emphasis */
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        a {
            color: #4f46e5; /* Horizon's secondary color */
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>New Contact Form Submission</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p>You have received a new contact form submission on your website. Below are the details:</p>
            <div class="details">
                <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= name %></p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
                <p><strong>Message:</strong> <%= message %></p>
            </div>
            <p>Please respond to this inquiry at your earliest convenience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>Â© 2025 Your Website. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>